ote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">中津静流</span> 说: 逻辑的基础是先验的（确信）<br>数学从某种意义上来讲隶属于逻辑，当然也是先验的，至于数学的起源不是物理，而是生产活动，但这一事实与数学的基础是什么，在我看来没有必然的联系。<br>补充一句，逻辑的基础是啥学术界...</q></div>我觉得逻辑这种东西仍然需要实践总结, 我们没法凭空创造出逻辑..不然是得不出有意义的结论的..<br>当然我也只是随口说说"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3490.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1439309","time":"2019-4-30 19:33","userId":"lhb5883","userName":"lhb5883-污🐱王VIP⑩","userSign":"(媛娇系是检验大法的唯一标准)","message":"形而上学","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1439316","time":"2019-4-30 19:42","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"(Q, Σ, Γ, δ, q0, Z0, F)","message":"与经验相对的是什么？大概是直觉。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/82/18215.jpg","floor":"#22-1","id":"1439731","time":"2019-5-2 05:22","userId":"utar","userName":"塔塔塔","userSign":"","message":"+1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/41/77/417772.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1439319","time":"2019-4-30 19:50","userId":"417772","userName":"905","userSign":"(Life's too short for chess.)","message":"问题在于“通过采用实践获得”的主体是人还是大脑还是意识与无意识的？","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/56/295606.jpg","floor":"#24","id":"1439327","time":"2019-4-30 19:57","userId":"295606","userName":"absurd","userSign":"(炸雞漢堡)","message":"沒經驗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#25","id":"1439333","time":"2019-4-30 20:01","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"(我们遇到什么 DD , 也不要怕 , 顶着面对它 , 消除单推 ...)","message":"童贞 ( 暴言 )","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/22/302247.jpg","floor":"#26","id":"1439337","time":"2019-4-30 20:27","userId":"302247","userName":"Mewtw0","userSign":"","message":"天资 直感","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/64/56424.jpg","floor":"#27","id":"1439341","time":"2019-4-30 20:36","userId":"muhan82","userName":"离群客","userSign":"(不知筋力衰多少，但觉新来懒上楼)","message":"演绎","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/96/49674.jpg","floor":"#28","id":"1439354","time":"2019-4-30 21:06","userId":"plus_1","userName":"空気力学少女","userSign":"(Panta Rhei)","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">历史</span><br>果然还是历史吧。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/45/25/452531.jpg","floor":"#29","id":"1439357","time":"2019-4-30 21:19","userId":"piglalala","userName":"piglalala","userSign":"(如果能被美少女包养该多好啊)","message":"人教版历史告诉我们文艺复兴中理性的思考与中方当时的经验为主的思想对立<br><br>好吧其实是我们那个博士生导师兼高考指导员历史老师说的","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/26/342667.jpg","floor":"#30","id":"1439367","time":"2019-4-30 21:36","userId":"342667","userName":"鋭ちゃん","userSign":"(随意。随己意。意怖，意不欲，意不安稳，不随。又不纵意。 . ...)","message":"形而上学","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/39/303997.jpg","floor":"#31","id":"1439368","time":"2019-4-30 21:49","userId":"sherlockshin","userName":"九條氏","userSign":"(円環の理を信じで。)","message":"未経験者（素人）→経験者（玄人）","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/69/6912.jpg","floor":"#32","id":"1439374","time":"2019-4-30 22:04","userId":"6912","userName":"tora","userSign":"(我们正和太阳并肩作战！)","message":"处男","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/68/226875.jpg","floor":"#33","id":"1439655","time":"2019-5-1 22:05","userId":"tides_","userName":"潮汐听雨","userSign":"(少年听雨歌楼上，红烛昏罗帐。)","message":"最近在看的一本科学哲学的书，从研究方法角度把直觉明确定义为经验的反义词。但我个人感觉从经验是感性认识这个角度来说，反义词是理性。<br><span style=\"color: gray;\"><span style=\"font-size:10px; line-height:10px;\">[来自Bangumi M1 for Android]</span></span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/98/69822.jpg","floor":"#34","id":"1439673","time":"2019-5-1 22:39","userId":"shadowdreamer","userName":"CureDovahkinn🤔","userSign":"(プリキュアなりたい)","message":"经验医学 <=> 循证医学","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/75/77515.jpg","floor":"#35","id":"1439749","time":"2019-5-2 09:36","userId":"th3ta","userName":"th3ta \"Paradox\"","userSign":"(Rigidity and Uncertainty~☆)","message":"看你是从那个方面定义经验了... 中文「经验」等价于英文「experience」，其中有两方面的意思：<br><br>一个是「Event(s) of which one is cognizant.」，类似于「个人对经历事件的记忆」，反义词应该是【理论】，这个理论可以是科学，也可以是伪科学/巫术/神学，只要能成体系就行...<br><br>另一个是「A collection of events and/or activities from which an individual or group may gather knowledge, opinions, and skills. And the knowledge thus gathered.」，类似于「实验」，所以反义词应该是【先验】，也就是不需要依赖后天感官记忆去获取，而先天就存在于人类内心之中的知识","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/93/449353.jpg","floor":"#36","id":"1439763","time":"2019-5-2 10:42","userId":"449353","userName":"爱在西元前","userSign":"(。。。)","message":"可以，这很哲学","sub":[]}]